column2: SELECT TOP #  s.plate,s.mjd,s.fiberid, p.score as score  FROM ..SpecObj as s  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbySpecObjEq(#,#,#) AS b ON b.SpecobjID = S.SpecobjID  JOIN Galaxy AS p ON s.bestobjid=p.objid  WHERE s.zWarning = # AND (p.u - p.g) > # AND (p.u - p.g) < # AND (p.flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) > #)
